      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.401 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) was asked about the reason for placing the palm branch (jareedah),\nImam (as) replied: \"Indeed, the punishment is averted from them (the deceased) as long as it remains fresh.\""
